{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1611957956.419921", "card_id": "Q_441805437", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1977}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待教育部答复「防止男性青少年女性化」提案，注重「阳刚之气」培养？什么才是「阳刚之气」，如何落实？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "教育部答复「防止男性青少年女性化」提案：注重「阳刚之气」培养"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-40c5330b7d3b9a9dfa77742b83e057b9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3002 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441805437"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIu5fDsba4rfdzEAMaCDYwNDU2OTEyIOaPzoAGMN8BOOIqQAByCTQ0MTgwNTQzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1611957956.4206254", "card_id": "Q_441757711", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1067}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 1 月 28 日美股游戏驿站 GME 被 Robinhood 等券商禁止买入，导致股价狂泻？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这样是否可以起诉券商？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-de213caa1bcaf6fd7b746b576fc68f9a_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2299 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441757711"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iu5fDsba4rfdzEAMaCDYwNDQ2MjY1IO3Ky4AGMFQ4mTBAAXIJNDQxNzU3NzExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1611957956.4211862", "card_id": "Q_441839927", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 183}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中方宣布不再承认所谓 BNO 护照作为旅行证件和身份证明，释放了怎样的信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在 29 日举行的外交部例行记者会上，有记者提问称，英国政府宣布自 1 月 31 日起，调整后的英国公民海外护照 (BNO) 及签证政策正式生效，请问中方对此有何评论？ 发言人赵立坚在回应中称，英方罔顾香港已经回归中国 24 年的事实，不顾中方严正立场，公然违背承诺，执意炮制出台所谓量身定制的具有英国国民海外 BNO 身份的香港居民，赴英居留和入籍政策，并一再扩大适用范围。英方试图把大批港人变成二等英国公民，已经彻底改变了原来中英谅解的 BNO 性质。 英国现在所谓的 BNO 已经不再是原来的 BNO，此举严重侵犯中国主权，粗暴干涉香港事务和中国内政，严重违反国际法和国际关系基本准则。中方对此强烈愤慨，坚决反对。 「自 1 月 31 日起，中方不再承认所谓的 BNO 护照作为旅行证件和身份证明，并保留采取进一步措施的权利。」赵立坚称。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-925faec42fc325cd13438aed329e7ab3_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1175 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441839927"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iu5fDsba4rfdzEAMaCDYwNDY0NTY2IIf6zoAGMA04qQxAAnIJNDQxODM5OTI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1611957956.4217176", "card_id": "Q_441864413", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 152}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待华融公司原董事长赖小民被执行死刑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "经最高人民法院核准，2021 年 1 月 29 日上午，天津市第二中级人民法院依照法定程序对赖小民执行了死刑。 2021 年 1 月 5 日，天津市第二中级人民法院以受贿罪、贪污罪和重婚罪，判处赖小民死刑，剥夺政治权利终身，并处没收个人全部财产。赖小民上诉后，天津市高级人民法院裁定驳回上诉，维持原判，并报请最高人民法院核准。 央视"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e72f874415e00202318c021ccf5bc275_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "775 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441864413"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iu5fDsba4rfdzEAMaCDYwNDY5OTUzIOu6z4AGMAo49QdAA3IJNDQxODY0NDEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1611957956.422179", "card_id": "Q_441882176", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 346}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价知乎《答案奇遇夜》晚会？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "知乎答案奇遇夜全程回放"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e64290ca509d8116f00d5e4a546ab6af_200x0.gif"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "741 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441882176"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIu5fDsba4rfdzEAMaCDYwNDczOTEzIMzxz4AGMCg4oAhABHIJNDQxODgyMTc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1611957956.422725", "c